^C7d THE STORY

^C00 Arpil 2006.In the country Korath the Korathian army led by Captain Justin Darian 
was a threat to the United Kingdom.An RAF war hero Joe Sentinel heard about a plot.


^P
^C7d THE STORY

^C6c He listened to the radio and heard Captain Darian's voice.The plot was to start 
a nuclear war against Britain.This was not allowed to happen.

^P
^C7d THE STORY

^C00 Captain Darian's scientists were building robots.They were scary and dangerous.The 
main machine was a squad of tank commandos.Captain Darian wanted a whole load to 
stick to each other and was going to help them destroy Britain.

^P
^C7d THE STORY

^C00 You hopped into your aircraft and was ready to fly off and stop him.The plot 
needed to be stopped and Darian defeated.
  
^C09You landed but the Korathians didn't notice.
  
^C6cYou were near the entry holding your shotgun.Barriers stood around you.

^P
^C7d THE STORY

