^C7d THE ENEMY

Korath Guard: ^C00Grunts of the Korath army.They carry pistols and are slow but weak.


^C7d Korath Scientist: ^C00Fast but easy to kill since they are anxious for the kill 
but never do it.

^C7d Korath Troop: ^C00Captain Darian's main soldiers.They are tough and are dangerous 
in groups.They carry double barrel rifles

^P
^C7d THE ENEMY

Korath Enforcer: ^C00Slow but dangerous.Dont punch them with your fist.They are highly 
trained.

^C7d Korath Patrol: ^C00They are seen quite often and they are fast and dangerous

  
^C7d Gladiator: ^C00Carry MP60 chainguns and can put a bullet in your head easily


^P
^C7d THE ENEMY

Tank: ^C00Huge robots that can be heard when they walk.Get in take out machinegun 
and keep firing

^C7d Tank Commando: ^C00Much more tough than a tank.These robots are fast so watch 
out for them when a tank dies

^P
^C7d THE ENEMY

Captain Darian: ^C00Leader of the Korath army.He is just weak.Thinks he can start 
a war but the answer is no.

